observations.recommendation:
We recommended that management comply with the reporting guidelines of COA Circular No. 2015-008, as follows:

Municipal Accountant compute the depreciation expense for depreciable component of the road network;
Provide the disclosure of Road Networks in the notes to the financial statements;
General Services Officer render a Report on Local Road Network at the end of the accounting period; and
Inventory Committee prepare the Report on the Physical Count of the Road Network System.

